          _key14:
            '\n #### Help \n - Select a pre-built SQL statement to query the range of people that can be selected. \n - These template files are stored in WF_SQLTemplate , you can use SELECT No,Name FROM WF_SQLTemplate WHERE SQLType=5 to query out these templates. \n - Maintain these templates in the form designer or manually. \n ',
