            _key11:
              '\n #### Help \n - Customisation: For each element in the form, you can personalise the settings. \n - Elements that can be customised: basic fields, components, slave forms, general attachments, image attachments. \n - \n #### Configuration Diagram \n - ! [Enter image description](. /resource/WF/Admin/AttrNode/FrmSln/Sln5/Img/FrmCtrlSlnSetting.png "Screenshot.png") \n ',
