      _key59:
        '\n I need to make a vehicle management form. \n The base information contains basic fields such as vehicle number, name, license plate number, vehicle type (car, construction vehicle, cleaning vehicle), please provide . \n The slave tables are as follows, please give the fields of each slave table. \n Vehicle Parts:\n Maintenance Records:\n Outbound Vehicle Records:\n ',
